description:
Add mcp__.* matcher entry to wantedMatchers in internal/cli/install.go.

Currently only the Bash matcher is installed. Per spec §3.1, both Bash and
mcp__.* matchers are required for full MCP tool mediation via hooks.

Add second fuseMatcherEntry:
```go
{
    Matcher: "mcp__.*",
    Hooks: []fuseHookEntry{
        {Type: "command", Command: "fuse hook evaluate", Timeout: 30},
    },
},
```

Acceptance: `fuse install claude` creates settings with both Bash and mcp__.* PreToolUse matchers.

```validation
{"content_check": {"file": "internal/cli/install.go", "pattern": "mcp__"}, "tests": "go test -race ./..."}
```
